@startuml
skinparam monochrome true
skinparam shadowing false

title Sequence Diagram: Trip Completion and Rating

actor Tourist
participant System
participant Driver

Tourist -> System: View Trip Status (Completed)
System --> Tourist: Confirm Completion
Tourist -> System: Rate Driver
Tourist -> System: Provide Feedback
System --> Driver: Notify New Rating/Feedback
Driver -> System: View Ratings/Feedback
@enduml
